This option allows you to effectively add a user or users to every member's 'Ignore List'. However, users in this list can still see their own posts and threads...<br />
<br />
Enter a list of userid numbers, separated by spaces (for example: 4 12 68 102).<br />
<br />If you change this option, you need to rebuild thread and then forum information <a href="misc.php">here</a>.